**Rules concerning junior entries:**

Age 15 and under must be accompanied by an adult (as a pair or trio).
Age 16 & 17 may run as a pair, or be accompanied by an adult (as a pair or trio).
Age 18+ may run as an individual.

If the event needs to be cancelled the [PFO Event Cancellation Policy](/information/event-cancellation-refund-policy) will apply.

## Facilities

Toilets and refreshments at the event centre.

Greenhill Bowling & Social Club have bar snacks and can offer Burnley's own Haffners Pies. Please indicate when entering if you are likely to buy a pie (circa £3). This is to ensure that the Club have sufficient stock on the night.

